Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:47.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103583,107587}All I can say is\Nwhat we have is true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:49.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108963,109756}Oh, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119265,121392}Are you forsaking our love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:05.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122268,125188}I'll never forget you, Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126314,128316}Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141496,146709}It was an old movie, but I know why\NMeimi's parents recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146793,148795}Yes, it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:32.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148961,152215}Gee, how I hope I find\Na love like that one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156386,158471}He kinda looked like Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159305,160598}Meimi, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160890,162350}Huh? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162475,166062}Let's go out and find us\Nsome fantastic boyfriends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166437,168981}Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:58.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173111,178116}The Platform of Love and Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183579,185039}And how was the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185498,187458}It was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187458,188543}It was so touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188960,190920}It was a true love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193297,195633}They fall in love\Ndespite their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195633,197510}But in the end, they part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197969,199387}Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199804,202890}The actor who played\NJoseph was so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205226,207645}How sickening.\NWhat's all this mush about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208980,211733}How dare you eavesdrop on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212316,213151}Humph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:37.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213609,217780}Why do girls always get so excited\Nwhen they talk about love and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218656,221117}You wouldn't understand\Nabout true love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221367,223411}And I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224454,225830}Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226080,229542}All you ever think\Nabout is St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229709,230668}What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230835,232378}Well, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232503,233546}Listen, I'm…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234088,235089}Yeah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236799,237592}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243347,244557}Asuka Jr. …
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252774,255985}You've traveled all of\NJapan on a bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256652,257737}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258029,261282}And I met Minako here in this city\Non the last leg of my trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264160,265203}How romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265453,267747}But then his bicycle…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286599,287892}Wow, that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288100,290645}Not really, if you\Nhave the determination…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290645,291771}you could do it as well, Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291854,292605}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293731,296651}Since you live in Japan,\Nyou can try it anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296818,298569}Then maybe I'll give it try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299028,301989}Still, I'm really glad I got to\Nmeet someone nice like you, Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302657,305785}I've met a lot of people along\Nthe way but none so nice as…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308371,309330}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312750,313918}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314001,315002}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339652,341279}Give me back my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342488,343698}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343990,345449}Please open this gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:46.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346200,346784}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349787,350621}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352415,353833}What is all the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:58.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354584,358045}Madame, these people\Nare demanding to be let in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362174,365261}A boy took John's bike\Nand went into the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:05.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365428,365970}That's why we…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366178,368180}Are you accusing\Nmy son Tatsuo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368723,369640}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372268,373477}You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373686,377607}Tatsuo has a first class American\Nbicycle, ordered especially for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378149,380443}My name is on that bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380651,381819}Please go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:22.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382153,382820}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382987,386198}I don't want to hear any more of\Nyour ridiculous accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386490,387867}Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:30.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390036,390703}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391329,394916}We went back several times,\Nbut no one would listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:39.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395833,399587}And since it concerns a child, John\Ndoesn't want the police involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:45.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400046,405885}That bike was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405885,407803}We'd been through good times\Nand bad times on our travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:54.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409680,414268}All we can do is wait for the boy to\Nreturn the bicycle on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415645,416771}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417521,418564}Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419273,421901}I'm sure our prayers\Nwill be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:07.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423945,427156}John and Minako.\NThey're in love, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427657,429033}Yes, you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429200,430660}Such a dramatic meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:16.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431702,436540}And their love will burn furiously,\Nonly to end in a sad parting of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437959,439710}Ah, Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441295,443464}Alright.\NI'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443756,445716}Only we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:31.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446884,451013}John is returning to America\Non the last flight this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451555,452682}We have to get it back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454350,455309}Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:39.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455518,459230}I'll do everything I can\Nin honor of their love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461023,462024}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464360,466070}Dad is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466445,469281}He insists on eating Oden tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472076,474078}Ah, this is my favorite…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474203,475287}I'll put a lot in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478499,481794}"I will be at the Ninomiya residence\Ntonight to retrieve a bicycle."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481794,482878}"St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489176,492054}How'd she know\Nthis was my favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493597,494890}Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503149,504859}Ruby, that's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507778,509739}Meimi, it's time for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510448,511365}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516162,518497}Yum. We're having Oden tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531510,532845}Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544607,547526}There, Ruby's aerial\Nmerry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548194,549945}Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551030,553115}Yes, you can use it\Nin your next magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554283,556994}Would you like\Nto be part of my show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573469,576097}Wow, look at all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577640,579141}Take whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582561,583938}And where's the bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584688,585689}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589610,591779}I don't care if that\Nbike gets stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591779,592822}Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594740,596867}But isn't it\Nsupposed to be special?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597535,598327}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599870,602665}If that's how you feel…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:06.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602665,606377}we should have given it\Nto that bothersome American.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607044,610297}What? Yeah that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:16.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612133,616470}Please take care of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624895,626856}Tatsuo Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627940,630359}Now, why would St. Tail\Nwant to steal this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641370,644665}Lord forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:50.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650045,650796}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653382,654466}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656844,658846}Three!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672610,675154}In order for John\Nto make his flight tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675571,678741}he must take the train by 9 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679533,680534}9 pm at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:21.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680993,681869}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684330,687750}May God's blessings be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:07.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723035,727081}Alright, I want this room and\Nthe house closely guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727706,728457}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747518,748519}It's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749937,752731}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761991,763158}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767037,768038}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:57.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777047,777965}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779008,780634}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781552,782553}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788559,791228}Taking what is not\Nyours is very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791603,793188}I don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793230,794481}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802573,803949}Now do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804867,806160}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806368,808370}It was so cool,\NI couldn't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808787,810497}So you stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810664,812082}Alright, you're forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819506,821300}St. Tail! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821467,824720}Now for the real Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830351,831352}What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831643,832561}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832770,834563}Somebody go check the fuse box!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834605,835689}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849078,850162}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850454,851455}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852623,853999}This is the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854083,855376}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865260,866345}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866720,868680}A bicycle that flies…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873769,875062}Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:42.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878690,882194}Now, I'll let the wind carry me\Nright to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887449,889326}What?! You're not going to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895749,897209}Bring the patrol car around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904049,906135}Oh yeah! I have an extra\Nballoon here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910556,912766}You're not getting away\Nthis time, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920399,921275}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922943,925028}I did it! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925737,927489}Asuka Jr., look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959229,960189}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963150,965319}Oh dear, I've got to\Nput Asuka Jr. down somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975329,976246}Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976371,977331}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993263,994765}I need to borrow your bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994848,995516}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007236,1009446}Excuse me, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010072,1012074}Let's see… it's 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012199,1013367}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015369,1017120}Hey… what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028257,1029466}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036932,1038934}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039768,1042145}Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042187,1043105}Tatsuo Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047526,1048777}It's that kid's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054741,1056702}Hey, who's John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065252,1067004}Hey! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071800,1073760}Phew. That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080892,1081852}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082311,1083854}I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089776,1091278}I don't know why,\Nbut I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096408,1098368}Oh no… I've got to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104082,1106209}That's… the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125729,1126855}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127856,1129816}I want you to come to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130525,1133695}I can't, John. It will\Njust make things harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134279,1137949}John… so that means\Nit was his bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140494,1143997}I didn't get my bike back,\Nbut I'm glad I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144373,1145457}I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150545,1151630}I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152923,1154049}It's yours John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154174,1155384}But who brought it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156551,1158512}Our prayers were answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159179,1162015}John, we'll meet again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162099,1163058}We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165102,1168522}I thought I'd never see\Nmy bike again, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169439,1171775}So I know you\Nand I will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175904,1176863}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181785,1182994}That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192629,1194214}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208186,1209479}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212941,1214109}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216278,1217362}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217446,1219281}What's the matter?\NYou look so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221366,1223285}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223326,1223952}What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223952,1225787}It wouldn't hurt you\Nto talk about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225954,1228123}Humph. It's only love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229624,1232919}Oh, so Asuka Jr. is\Nin love with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233420,1234421}Listen, you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236882,1237924}We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238008,1238800}Oh, no!
